          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Situation A. Brandon&#x27;s, Sofia&#x27;s, and Kaedon&#x27;s Strategies</strong></p><p>Brandon, Sofia, and Kaedon used different strategies to answer the questions n the Initial Challenge. Is it possible to use each strategy to answer the questions? Explain.</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      [
        {
          "id": "SMJu7gHN5XWw5iQR",
          "title": "Text 7",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<li>Brandon&#x27;s Strategy</li><li>I used a rate table to find the unit rate for 1 box. I then used the unit rate to find other amounts.</li>"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "conXxk9nlJS8NE6O",
          "content": {
            "type": "Table",
            "columnWidths": {
              "Aw64iC-7qYPrztkt": 112.52841186523438,
              "wJYPkGAI-kYsrc1Q": 106.50213623046875
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "id": "E_mEMNn1zoLjYrxY",
          "title": "Text 3",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Sofia&#x27;s Strategy</p><p>I used multiples of the ratio that is given.</p><p>6 boxes for $48,</p><p>12 boxes for $96,</p><p>and 18 boxes for $144,</p><p>etc.</p>"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "jWTrQFmi2uGpNE09",
          "title": "Text 10",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Kaedon&#x27;s Strategy</p><p>I used an algebraic representation to find the costs <em>C</em> of selling <em>N</em> boxes of smoothie bars.</p><p><em>C</em> = 8<em>N</em></p>"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      {
        "id": "yljmeqLO3jJBgk1S",
        "title": "Text 8",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Student answers will vary. All three strategies are related to ratio relationships. All three strategies can be used to answer the questions.</p><p>Possible answers:</p><p><strong>Brandon&#x27;s Strategy</strong></p><p>Equivalent ratios can be found on the table using the multiples and factors of the two quantities.</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "YguB3-rsZ3sdiw5Q",
        "title": "Brandon's Strategy",
        "display": "teacher",
