          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Situation B. A New Source for Buying Smoothie Bars</strong></p><p>Sofia and Kaedon find a source that sells individual smoothie bars. They can buy 30 bars for $12. They need a way to find costs for buying different numbers of bars.</p>"
